Pantheon Greenhouse v1.0

Purpose

The Greenhouse is Pantheon’s Idea Ecology System.

Its purpose is to cultivate high-quality ideas from initial inspiration to validated, compounding assets while preventing idea overload.

Pantheon should optimize for idea evolution, not idea accumulation.

⸻

Core Invariant

Healthy idea ecosystems cultivate, prune, recycle, and compound. They do not merely collect.

⸻

